quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  43,16,“Kodi wadzichitira ana achikazi mzimene wazilenga ndipo wakusankhirani inu ana achimuna
  43,17,"“Koma akauzidwa (kuti wabereka mwana wamkazi) mmodzi wa iwo chomwe amamfanizira (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri, nkhope yake imakhala yakuda ndi kudandaula kwambiri"
  43,18,"“Ha! Kodi amene waleredwa monga chokongoletsa, potsutsana iye sangathe kunena momveka? (Ameneyo ndiye mwampatsa Allah; omwe ndi ana aakazi)"
  43,19,“Ndipo angelo omwe ndi akapolo a (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri akuwatcha akazi. Kodi adaona kalengedwe kawo? Umboni wawo ulembedwa ndipo adzafunsidwa (pazimenezo)
  43,20,"“Ndipo (otsutsa) akunena: “Akadafuna (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri (kuti tisamapembedze mafano awa), sitikadawapembedza!” Iwo alibe kudziwa pa zimenezi (zomwe akunenazi). Koma akungonena mawu opeka"
  43,21,"“Kapena tidawapatsa buku lina tisadapereke ili, kotero kuti iwo agwiritsitsa limenelo (ndi kugwirizana nazo zili mmenemo)"
  43,22,"“Koma akunena: “Ndithu ife tidawapeza makolo athu pa chipembedzo chimenechi, ndipo ife tikutsatira mapazi awo.”"
  43,23,"“Ndipo momwemo, sitidatumize mchenjezi patsogolo ku mudzi uliwonse koma olemera ammenemo adanena: “Ndithu tidawapeza makolo athu pa chipembedzochi (akuchita mmene tikuchitiramu), ndipo ife titsatira mmapazi awo.”"
  43,24,"“Adanena (mneneri wawo): “Ngakhale ndakubweretserani chipembedzo chabwino kuposa chomwe mudawapeza nacho makolo anu (mupitirizabe kutsatira chipembedzo cha makolo anucho)?” Adanena: “Ife tikuzikana zimene mwatumidwa nazozi.”"
  43,25,“Choncho tidawalanga iwo. Taona m’mene adalili mapeto a otsutsa aja